BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:McCormormick's Creek 5K\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260418T083000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260418T083000
UID:e41025376608e4ec6de182207885af74@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:Register online at: https://runsignup.com/.../Spencer/FriendsM
 cCormicksCreek5k This is a Mag 7 Series Race. Those registered and paid by
  March 15th(by mail) or April 3rd(online) will receive a race shirt. Shirt
 s available after that while supplies last. Packet Pick Up: 7:00-8:15am at
  the Nature Center Race starts promptly at 8:30am Awards following the rac
 e. Prizes to top male and female 5K overall runners and walkers. Awards gr
 anted to top 2 age group winners in 5K run and first age group winners in 
 5K walk. ***NEW THIS YEAR: Post-race Pancakes and Sausage Breakfast availa
 ble for $5. Please purchase by 4/15/2026 so we know how much to buy. All p
 roceeds from the race and the breakfast will be used to develop and suppor
 t projects and events that help preserve\, restore\, manage\, and interpre
 t the natural and cultural heritage and recreational opportunities of McCo
 rmick&rsquo\;s Creek State Park
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, 250 McCormick's Creek Park Road\, 
 Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:on.in.gov/mccormickscreek
X-SOURCE:McCormick's Creek State Park
END:VEVENT
